---
import ServiceLayout from '../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';

const title = 'Education Cleaning Dallas: School & University Cleaning | Commercial Cleaning Services of Dallas';
const description = 'Education cleaning services in Dallas, TX. School and university cleaning for healthy learning environments.';
const serviceName = 'Educational Facility Cleaning Services';
const targetKeyword = 'education cleaning dallas';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: 'What types of educational facilities do you clean?',
    answer: 'We clean K-12 schools, universities, colleges, daycare centers, preschools, and educational facilities. We address classrooms, gyms, cafeterias, libraries, laboratories, and administrative spaces.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Do you clean during school hours or after hours?',
    answer: 'We offer both options. Many schools prefer after-hours cleaning to avoid disrupting classes. We can also provide day porter services during school hours to address spills, restroom checks, and immediate cleaning needs.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Can you clean specialized areas like labs and gyms?',
    answer: 'Yes. We clean specialized school areas including science labs, computer labs, art rooms, gymnasiums, locker rooms, cafeterias, and auditoriums. Each space has specific requirements that we address appropriately.'
  },
  {
    question: 'Do you follow specific protocols for schools?',
    answer: 'Yes. We understand school schedules, security requirements, and the need to work around school activities. Our staff undergoes background checks appropriate for school environments.'
  },
  {
    question: 'What is included in school cleaning?',
    answer: 'Our education cleaning includes classroom desk and surface cleaning, trash removal, floor vacuuming and mopping, restroom cleaning and restocking, cafeteria and kitchen area cleaning, gym cleaning, locker room cleaning, and common area maintenance.'
  },
  {
    question: 'How often should schools be cleaned?',
    answer: 'Daily cleaning is standard for most schools with student attendance. High-traffic areas like cafeterias, gyms, and restrooms may require multiple daily service. We also provide periodic deep cleaning during breaks and summer for comprehensive maintenance.'
  }
];

const relatedServices = [
  {
    slug: 'janitorial-services',
    title: 'Janitorial Services Dallas',
    description: 'Recurring commercial cleaning services.'
  },
  {
    slug: 'comprehensive-cleaning',
    title: 'Comprehensive Cleaning Dallas',
    description: 'Complete facility services and deep cleaning.'
  },
  {
    slug: 'religious-building-cleaning',
    title: 'Religious Building Cleaning Dallas',
    description: 'Church and temple cleaning services.'
  }
];
---

<ServiceLayout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  serviceName={serviceName}
  targetKeyword={targetKeyword}
  faqs={faqs}
  relatedServices={relatedServices}
  parentPage="Services"
  heroImage="/images/Services/education-cleaning.webp"
>
  <p>
    Educational facilities require cleaning that goes beyond appearanceâ€”it affects the health and learning environment of students and staff. <strong>Education cleaning in Dallas</strong> addresses classrooms, cafeterias, gyms, restrooms, and all spaces that contribute to your educational mission.
  </p>

  <p>
    Schools, universities, and daycare centers have unique cleaning requirements due to high traffic, diverse spaces, and health considerations. Our education cleaning services address these needs while working around school schedules, security protocols, and operational requirements.
  </p>

  <h2>Classroom and Educational Space Cleaning</h2>

  <p>
    Classrooms are the primary learning spaces in schools. Our cleaning maintains these environments for student focus and teacher effectiveness.
  </p>

  <h3>Desk and Surface Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    We clean student desks, tables, chairs, and work surfaces, removing accumulated soil, fingerprints, and marks. This includes detailed wiping and disinfecting as appropriate for grade level and subject areas.
  </p>

  <h3>Floor Care in Classrooms</h3>
  <p>
    Classroom floors include carpet, tile, and other materials. We vacuum carpets thoroughly, mop hard floors, and address stains and spots. Floor care in classrooms helps extend flooring life and maintains appearance.
  </p>

  <h3>Whiteboard and Chalkboard Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Teaching walls require regular cleaning. We clean whiteboards, chalkboards, and presentation surfaces, removing marker residue, chalk dust, and accumulated residue. Clean presentation surfaces support effective teaching.
  </p>

  <h2>School Common Area Cleaning</h2>

  <p>
    Schools have numerous common areas that require coordinated cleaning attention.
  </p>

  <h3>Library and Media Center Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Libraries and media centers require careful cleaning around books, electronics, and media. We dust shelves, clean computer areas, and maintain these quiet study spaces with minimal disruption.
  </p>

  <h3>Administrative Office Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    School offices house administrative staff, counselors, and administrators. We clean these spaces thoroughly including desks, surfaces, floors, and common areas. Professional presentation supports your educational mission.
  </p>

  <h3>Hallway and Common Area Maintenance</h3>
  <p>
    School hallways see constant student traffic. We clean these high-traffic areas by vacuuming or mopping floors, dusting lockers and walls, cleaning trash receptacles, and addressing spots and stains.
  </p>

  <h3>Cafeteria and Kitchen Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    School cafeterias require cleaning that addresses food service, dining areas, and food preparation spaces. We clean dining tables and chairs, floors, serving lines, and trash areas. We work around food service schedules and maintain appropriate hygiene standards.
  </p>

  <h3>Gymnasium and Locker Room Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    School gyms and locker rooms see heavy use from physical education and sports. We clean gym floors, locker rooms, shower areas, and fitness equipment. We address sweat and soil accumulation while maintaining equipment.
  </p>

  <h2>Specialized Educational Facility Cleaning</h2>

  <p>
    Educational facilities include specialized spaces that require particular cleaning approaches.
  </p>

  <h3>Science Lab and Computer Lab Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Science laboratories require cleaning around chemicals, glassware, and equipment. We clean lab benches, sinks, countertops, and floors while being careful around chemicals and equipment. Computer labs require careful cleaning of keyboards, mice, monitors, and work surfaces.
  </p>

  <h3>Art Room Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Art rooms accumulate paint, clay, and art materials. We clean tables, sinks, storage areas, and floors while addressing these specialized materials. Appropriate cleaning methods protect art supplies and equipment.
  </p>

  <h3>Music Room Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Music rooms contain instruments, sheet music, and audio equipment. We clean these spaces carefully, cleaning floors and surfaces while protecting musical instruments and equipment from damage.
  </p>

  <h3>Daycare and Preschool Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Daycare centers and preschools require enhanced cleaning for health and safety. We clean classrooms, nap areas, play areas, and restrooms with attention to sanitization. We use child-safe products and methods appropriate for early childhood environments.
  </p>

  <h3>University and College Cleaning</h3>
  <p>
    Colleges and universities include not just classrooms but also laboratories, lecture halls, dormitories, and student centers. We clean these diverse spaces while working around university schedules and events.
  </p>

  <h2>Dallas Education Cleaning Coverage</h2>

  <p>
    Our education cleaning services cover Dallas and Dallas County educational facilities. We clean schools and learning centers in Dallas, Highland Park, University Park, Farmers Branch, Irving, Garland, Richardson, Mesquite, Carrollton, and Addison.
  </p>

  <p>
    Contact us to discuss education cleaning for your Dallas educational facility. We'll develop a cleaning program that supports your learning environment.
  </p>
</ServiceLayout>
